664
00:27:01,367 --> 00:27:03,200
I'm trying to avoid
jargon, but I inevitably

665
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:04,110
end up using jargon.

666
00:27:04,110 --> 00:27:07,070
I realize that, as I just
said that VPN, Virtual Private

667
00:27:07,070 --> 00:27:09,120
Network, not necessarily
for right now,

668
00:27:09,120 --> 00:27:11,750
but it's just another
thing to note.

669
00:27:11,750 --> 00:27:14,300
So we're going to allow
SSH traffic from anywhere

670
00:27:14,300 --> 00:27:15,690
to just keep it simple.

671
00:27:15,690 --> 00:27:18,410
We're not doing anything
sensitive on these EC2 instances

672
00:27:18,410 --> 00:27:18,910
anyway.

673
00:27:18,910 --> 00:27:22,070
So it's not a big deal.

674
00:27:22,070 --> 00:27:23,550
Configuring storage.

