into the computer, right?

681
00:27:39,150 --> 00:27:42,710
You machine, it has some default
amount of storage or memory

682
00:27:42,710 --> 00:27:43,410
on it.

683
00:27:43,410 --> 00:27:45,920
And you're like, well, I want
to have an external hard drive

