701
00:28:27,852 --> 00:28:30,060
it'll give you the option
to just delete both of them

702
00:28:30,060 --> 00:28:30,940
right away.

703
00:28:30,940 --> 00:28:33,450
But if you create it
separately and just delete

704
00:28:33,450 --> 00:28:35,250
