need to spin it back up again.

765
00:31:10,720 --> 00:31:14,180
Terminate means I just
delete it entirely.

766
00:31:14,180 --> 00:31:15,608
Termination protection.

767
00:31:15,608 --> 00:31:17,900
If, for example, you're
working with a team or a larger

